WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:14.740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

00:00:29.995 --> 00:00:34.031
(Azure Spring)

00:00:34.032 --> 00:00:36.667
(All characters, places, events, etc. depicted are fictional.)

00:00:36.668 --> 00:00:39.037
(Children and animals were filmed under strict guidelines.)

00:01:01.993 --> 00:01:02.994
So?

00:01:03.495 --> 00:01:06.431
Any thoughts after your first harvest, baby free diver?

00:01:10.035 --> 00:01:11.535
I loved it.

00:01:11.536 --> 00:01:13.536
So much so that I couldn't think of anything else.

00:01:16.341 --> 00:01:18.376
Didn't you like it a lot?

00:01:19.010 --> 00:01:20.011
What?

00:01:20.712 --> 00:01:22.379
She felt so good...

00:01:22.380 --> 00:01:25.550
that she took back calling me rude and even said I was like the sea.

00:01:26.284 --> 00:01:29.020
What? The sea?

00:01:29.487 --> 00:01:31.722
Darn it. Were you flirting with him?

00:01:31.723 --> 00:01:33.091
You said you weren't interested!

00:01:33.391 --> 00:01:36.026
What? Wait. No way!

00:01:36.027 --> 00:01:37.429
I never said...

00:01:38.496 --> 00:01:39.930
Keep it quiet.

00:01:39.931 --> 00:01:41.166
What's going on?

00:01:43.001 --> 00:01:44.102
Did you just smile?

00:01:44.369 --> 00:01:46.370
Hey!

00:01:46.371 --> 00:01:48.073
Where do you think you're going? Sit down.

00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:51.108
- What is really going on? - I swear.

00:01:51.109 --> 00:01:53.478
It wasn't like that.

00:01:54.012 --> 00:01:56.181
If it wasn't that, then what was it?

00:01:56.815 --> 00:01:58.016
Jeez.

00:01:58.517 --> 00:02:00.818
You're smiling? Did you just smile?

00:02:00.819 --> 00:02:03.221
I loved that the sea was there.

00:02:08.793 --> 00:02:11.996
Nothing's going on. I mean it.

00:02:11.997 --> 00:02:14.399
Why are you doing this to me?

00:02:14.666 --> 00:02:17.469
- So what's going on? - Nothing!

00:02:17.869 --> 00:02:18.970
Did you just smile?

00:02:20.939 --> 00:02:23.375
- I'm done. - Come on.

00:02:29.915 --> 00:02:32.050
(Jung Gi Tae)

00:02:49.134 --> 00:02:52.137
(Republic of Korea Army Park Jae Hui)

00:03:07.786 --> 00:03:13.792
(Episode 4: Secret of the Deep Sea)

00:03:17.362 --> 00:03:18.363
Excuse...

00:03:19.664 --> 00:03:21.399
Hey, you call him out.

00:03:23.935 --> 00:03:27.005
Duk Hyun, dinner's ready. Come on out.

00:03:38.450 --> 00:03:39.451
Sit over here.

00:03:46.791 --> 00:03:48.293
I don't eat anything raw.

00:03:49.327 --> 00:03:52.931
What? You're a free diver. How can you not eat raw seafood?

00:03:54.065 --> 00:03:55.900
Eating seafood raw can expose you...

00:03:55.901 --> 00:03:58.021
- to parasites and bacterial infections... - Open up.

00:04:00.338 --> 00:04:01.540
Chew on it.

00:04:02.274 --> 00:04:04.776
You'll taste more of the ocean than when it's boiled.

00:04:17.556 --> 00:04:18.723
Well, it is dangerous...

00:04:20.659 --> 00:04:23.328
because it's so good and could get you addicted.

00:04:24.129 --> 00:04:25.130
Right?

00:04:27.365 --> 00:04:31.469
Try a piece of turban snail. It's chewy and tender.

00:04:47.586 --> 00:04:49.287
Yes, it's good.

00:04:51.890 --> 00:04:53.491
- Cheers. - Cheers.

00:05:00.765 --> 00:05:01.800
Duk Hyun.

00:05:04.069 --> 00:05:05.704
I look flushed, don't I?

00:05:08.373 --> 00:05:10.475
But why do you talk to him like he's older than you?

00:05:11.443 --> 00:05:12.803
You don't even know how old he is.

00:05:12.944 --> 00:05:14.212
Because...

00:05:15.013 --> 00:05:16.882
he's good-looking.

00:05:18.149 --> 00:05:22.020
Then should everyone who's ugly be considered younger?

00:05:28.126 --> 00:05:30.161
Hey, now that you're considered younger than me,

00:05:30.829 --> 00:05:32.264
let me ask you this.

00:05:33.865 --> 00:05:35.467
My dear younger friend,

00:05:36.535 --> 00:05:37.775
why did you become a free diver?

00:05:45.810 --> 00:05:46.811
Because I can...

00:05:48.213 --> 00:05:49.514
be alone.

00:05:54.085 --> 00:05:55.187
I must be alone.

00:05:55.754 --> 00:05:56.922
That's why I harvest seafood.

00:06:00.926 --> 00:06:01.993
It was unexpected.

00:06:03.361 --> 00:06:05.263
I thought I had a grasp of who he was.

00:06:07.032 --> 00:06:09.801
A lonely man's elegant hobby.

00:06:14.806 --> 00:06:16.308
That's way too sexy.

00:06:17.042 --> 00:06:19.611
He's so fatally charming.

00:06:20.011 --> 00:06:22.180
Hey. Go home, Su Jeong.

00:06:22.547 --> 00:06:23.548
You're drunk.

00:06:25.851 --> 00:06:28.019
It's way too late for me to go home alone.

00:06:29.154 --> 00:06:31.288
- Can you walk me home... - Have a safe walk back.

00:06:31.289 --> 00:06:32.891
What? Duk Hyun...

00:06:35.627 --> 00:06:36.995
Wait, Duk Hyun!

00:06:38.897 --> 00:06:40.498
He may be much darker and deeper,

00:06:41.266 --> 00:06:42.434
just like...

00:06:43.068 --> 00:06:44.536
the deep sea.

00:06:52.410 --> 00:06:53.578
Jeez.

00:06:54.012 --> 00:06:57.015
I wanted to walk home with Duk Hyun.

00:06:57.716 --> 00:06:59.996
Why are you interested in someone you know nothing about?

00:07:00.652 --> 00:07:02.287
What if he's dangerous?

00:07:03.121 --> 00:07:04.990
I've known him for three years now.

00:07:05.257 --> 00:07:08.859
He's been quietly harvesting food not for one or two years,

00:07:08.860 --> 00:07:11.396
but three whole years. No way he's dangerous.

00:07:11.830 --> 00:07:15.367
That's why all the rumours have disappeared.

00:07:16.001 --> 00:07:17.802
There were rumours about him?

00:07:18.370 --> 00:07:19.971
So many of them.

00:07:20.305 --> 00:07:22.440
Some said he was an agent who left in disgrace,

00:07:22.841 --> 00:07:24.801
others that he was a murderer just out of prison,

00:07:25.076 --> 00:07:28.613
or a hidden child of a conglomerate family, and many more.

00:07:29.147 --> 00:07:33.251
At first, he was an extremely suspicious man.

00:07:33.919 --> 00:07:34.986
But now...

00:07:39.224 --> 00:07:40.258
Suspicious.

00:07:47.265 --> 00:07:48.333
He seems...

00:07:50.468 --> 00:07:51.469
very suspicious.

00:07:51.903 --> 00:07:52.904
Yes.

00:08:02.147 --> 00:08:03.447
- Who is that? - Darn it.

00:08:03.448 --> 00:08:04.949
I've never seen him before.

00:08:04.950 --> 00:08:05.951
Jeez.

00:08:10.121 --> 00:08:11.756
No, don't go. Watch out.

00:08:17.796 --> 00:08:20.632
Darn it. Where is it?

00:08:24.503 --> 00:08:25.604
Jeez.

00:08:54.165 --> 00:08:56.801
Did he start a family with a free diver, or did he become one?

00:08:57.102 --> 00:08:58.136
What the heck?

00:09:26.231 --> 00:09:27.511
What's he going to do with that?

00:09:28.366 --> 00:09:29.534
Wait, is he...

00:09:30.635 --> 00:09:31.803
a robber?

00:09:32.103 --> 00:09:36.174
- No way. - Where are you, Yoon Duk Hyun?

00:09:38.410 --> 00:09:39.444
No!

00:09:39.678 --> 00:09:40.779
Hey, be quiet.

00:09:42.514 --> 00:09:43.615
He must be...

00:09:44.249 --> 00:09:46.785
someone who holds a grudge against Duk Hyun.

00:09:47.819 --> 00:09:50.589
I think he's here to kill him. What do we do?

00:09:51.122 --> 00:09:52.424
What are we going to do?

00:09:53.158 --> 00:09:54.292
What now?

00:09:56.428 --> 00:09:57.529
Hey, you punk!

00:10:01.066 --> 00:10:02.200
Who the heck are you?

00:10:03.335 --> 00:10:05.170
Get out of my place!

00:10:06.972 --> 00:10:09.040
- My goodness. - You!

00:10:09.941 --> 00:10:10.976
What the heck?

00:10:16.314 --> 00:10:17.315
What on earth?

00:10:19.918 --> 00:10:21.186
Seo An Na!

00:10:23.655 --> 00:10:24.923
An Na!

00:10:38.103 --> 00:10:39.137
You're up.

00:10:40.105 --> 00:10:42.107
What happened?

00:10:42.541 --> 00:10:44.341
I thought you had fainted after falling,

00:10:44.342 --> 00:10:46.182
but you began to snore, so I moved you inside.

00:10:47.979 --> 00:10:49.247
Oh, thanks.

00:10:50.615 --> 00:10:53.450
But a suspicious guy grabbed a hook,

00:10:53.451 --> 00:10:55.387
- trying to kill... - Are you talking about me?

00:10:56.655 --> 00:10:58.223
Yes, I'm talking about him!

00:11:00.825 --> 00:11:02.427
I warned you. Get lost.

00:11:03.695 --> 00:11:07.599
I wouldn't be here now if I were scared of your warning.

00:11:11.336 --> 00:11:13.003
Are you two acquainted?

00:11:13.004 --> 00:11:14.172
- No. - Yes.

00:11:14.739 --> 00:11:15.740
Excuse me?

00:11:16.775 --> 00:11:19.444
We are acquainted. He's just pouting.

00:11:20.679 --> 00:11:24.683
Anyway, why do you keep talking casually with me?

00:11:25.217 --> 00:11:27.052
What? Are you older than me?

00:11:29.621 --> 00:11:30.622
It looks like it.

00:11:33.625 --> 00:11:35.460
Yes, I'm older. So what?

00:11:36.528 --> 00:11:38.663
I'm casual with anyone within a ten-year age gap.

00:11:43.168 --> 00:11:45.269
Why do you do that, hiding on an island like this?

00:11:45.270 --> 00:11:46.371
Mind your own business.

00:11:47.072 --> 00:11:48.240
"Mind your own business."

00:11:48.940 --> 00:11:51.208
Why? Do you want to get better at diving...

00:11:51.209 --> 00:11:52.777
and flee overseas?

00:11:53.812 --> 00:11:55.146
Learn to drive a ship instead.

00:11:57.482 --> 00:11:58.483
"Flee"?

00:11:58.783 --> 00:11:59.985
You didn't know?

00:12:00.986 --> 00:12:03.188
He came here to avoid me and...

00:12:04.823 --> 00:12:05.857
Enough is enough.

00:12:09.961 --> 00:12:11.801
Aren't you going to grab your harvesting gear?

00:12:12.030 --> 00:12:13.031
Me?

00:12:13.231 --> 00:12:14.633
Were you going to quit after a day?

00:12:15.433 --> 00:12:16.468
Whatever suits you.

00:12:17.903 --> 00:12:19.905
Why is he taking this out on me?

00:12:20.338 --> 00:12:21.540
Hey, wait up!

00:12:36.555 --> 00:12:39.357
Did you do something wrong where you came from?

00:12:39.925 --> 00:12:41.358
He said you fled, so I just...

00:12:41.359 --> 00:12:42.427
Do I seem different now?

00:12:42.994 --> 00:12:44.062
It's kind of odd.

00:12:44.596 --> 00:12:46.398
And I got curious, too.

00:12:52.070 --> 00:12:53.671
Who I was or what I did doesn't change...

00:12:53.672 --> 00:12:56.474
the fact that I'm your tenant and diving teacher.

00:12:58.476 --> 00:13:00.879
Well, that's true.

00:13:01.079 --> 00:13:02.113
Then let's hurry.

00:13:02.814 --> 00:13:04.382
We have to go far today to get oysters.

00:13:09.721 --> 00:13:11.756
Does simply knowing someone through and through...

00:13:12.891 --> 00:13:14.092
create trust?

00:13:27.672 --> 00:13:28.807
If that were the case,

00:13:30.108 --> 00:13:31.810
I would've had faith in myself first.

00:13:37.582 --> 00:13:39.851
You can start again now.

00:13:47.225 --> 00:13:48.226
Trust...

00:13:49.327 --> 00:13:50.862
does not come from knowledge.

00:13:53.965 --> 00:13:55.734
Maybe the reason I chase after him...

00:13:56.568 --> 00:13:59.171
is to find out when that trust will come.

00:14:02.207 --> 00:14:03.208
Oysters?

00:14:03.842 --> 00:14:06.845
He can find oysters in the middle of summer?

00:14:09.614 --> 00:14:10.749
Wait up!

00:14:24.663 --> 00:14:26.131
We have to get on a boat?

00:14:39.477 --> 00:14:41.046
I'm here, Duk Hyun!

00:14:42.380 --> 00:14:44.916
- What's going on? - Are you coming too, Su Jeong?

00:14:45.250 --> 00:14:47.352
I'd follow Duk Hyun anywhere.

00:14:49.020 --> 00:14:50.388
Everybody is here now.

00:14:50.856 --> 00:14:52.357
Dad, we're good to go!

00:14:54.492 --> 00:14:56.862
Hang on tightly. We're off!

00:14:57.996 --> 00:14:59.030
Wait!

00:15:04.369 --> 00:15:06.338
Are you coming, too?

00:15:08.039 --> 00:15:09.040
We're friends after all.

00:15:21.453 --> 00:15:22.687
Let's go!

00:16:14.573 --> 00:16:16.274
How far are we going?

00:16:17.375 --> 00:16:18.410
We're almost there.

00:16:20.779 --> 00:16:22.214
I can't do this anymore.

00:16:50.175 --> 00:16:52.335
The Black Snake Unit's Water Ghost still got his game.

00:16:56.181 --> 00:16:57.215
Duk Hyun,

00:16:57.649 --> 00:16:58.984
I'm dizzy.

00:17:00.585 --> 00:17:01.853
We have to get to that side.

00:17:02.721 --> 00:17:04.322
What? No way...

00:17:40.292 --> 00:17:41.293
Oh, gosh.

00:17:46.264 --> 00:17:47.265
An Na.

00:17:48.466 --> 00:17:51.703
Doesn't Duk Hyun seem suspicious?

00:17:53.338 --> 00:17:55.340
Didn't you call him sexy and mysterious before?

00:17:55.740 --> 00:17:56.975
It's not that.

00:17:57.876 --> 00:18:00.645
Ever since that new guy came,

00:18:01.146 --> 00:18:03.181
his face hasn't been the same.

00:18:03.515 --> 00:18:04.916
I can tell just by looking at him.

00:18:10.021 --> 00:18:11.056
Maybe you're right.

00:18:12.657 --> 00:18:13.925
I'm telling you.

00:18:14.860 --> 00:18:15.961
Something's fishy.

00:18:46.391 --> 00:18:47.392
What's going on?

00:18:59.538 --> 00:19:00.539
Is this it?

00:19:01.206 --> 00:19:02.406
Is this where the oysters are?

00:19:05.277 --> 00:19:07.445
We must cross over to that island to harvest oysters.

00:19:11.917 --> 00:19:13.118
But this is the sea.

00:19:13.552 --> 00:19:15.353
How are we going to get there?

00:19:17.155 --> 00:19:19.858
If we wait, the sea will open a path for us.

00:19:20.792 --> 00:19:23.528
Jeez, are we waiting for the miracle of Moses?

00:19:24.796 --> 00:19:26.097
Enough with your nonsense.

00:19:26.731 --> 00:19:27.732
Hey.

00:19:29.267 --> 00:19:30.735
Let's go over there and look around.

00:19:32.404 --> 00:19:35.973
What? But I want to stay here.

00:19:35.974 --> 00:19:36.975
Come.

00:19:37.275 --> 00:19:38.577
Duk Hyun...

00:20:07.272 --> 00:20:08.540
How's your shoulder?

00:20:10.175 --> 00:20:11.276
How did you know?

00:20:13.612 --> 00:20:17.015
You said it in your sleep at the public clinic last time...

00:20:18.917 --> 00:20:22.187
that your shoulder is fully healed, but you don't think you can swim again.

00:20:26.358 --> 00:20:27.492
Oh, gosh.

00:20:33.231 --> 00:20:34.299
You're right.

00:20:35.867 --> 00:20:36.968
To be honest,

00:20:38.336 --> 00:20:39.538
I'm not unwell.

00:20:42.107 --> 00:20:43.875
I was fine while harvesting seafood,

00:20:45.777 --> 00:20:46.857
and even the doctor said...

00:20:47.579 --> 00:20:49.681
I could go back to swimming ages ago.

00:20:53.818 --> 00:20:56.288
- I know, but... - But faith...

00:20:57.722 --> 00:20:59.224
doesn't come from knowledge.

00:21:04.396 --> 00:21:05.397
Then...

00:21:07.365 --> 00:21:08.533
what can I do...

00:21:10.001 --> 00:21:11.736
to have faith in myself?

00:21:17.576 --> 00:21:19.411
Give yourself time...

00:21:21.713 --> 00:21:23.648
until you can learn to trust yourself again.

00:21:28.753 --> 00:21:29.788
All things...

00:21:30.288 --> 00:21:31.656
need time.

00:21:45.036 --> 00:21:46.137
It opened up.

00:21:48.373 --> 00:21:50.842
The sea opened up!

00:22:17.202 --> 00:22:19.237
What? It really...

00:22:20.238 --> 00:22:21.239
opened up.

00:22:24.576 --> 00:22:25.577
Let's go.

00:22:29.181 --> 00:22:30.282
- Let's go. - Okay.

00:23:00.378 --> 00:23:01.658
(Parang-ri Haenyeo Cho Mi Hyeon)

00:23:09.120 --> 00:23:11.890
The sea will be different from the one we dived in last time.

00:23:17.996 --> 00:23:18.997
I can tell.

00:23:19.731 --> 00:23:21.099
It must be quite deep.

00:23:21.933 --> 00:23:23.268
It's very deep and dark.

00:23:24.836 --> 00:23:25.837
Stick out your hand.

00:23:31.743 --> 00:23:33.345
That's how far you can see.

00:23:34.713 --> 00:23:35.814
Then...

00:23:36.348 --> 00:23:37.749
how do you harvest seafood?

00:23:39.384 --> 00:23:40.385
By faith.

00:23:43.088 --> 00:23:44.648
Trust the training you've had so far...

00:23:45.690 --> 00:23:46.725
and...

00:23:47.325 --> 00:23:49.461
the memories from your previous diving experiences.

00:25:37.369 --> 00:25:38.370
But...

00:25:39.204 --> 00:25:40.705
can we really find oysters here?

00:25:55.720 --> 00:25:59.124
Rock oysters only live in the far and deep sea.

00:26:03.962 --> 00:26:05.864
Is it like a legend?

00:26:08.800 --> 00:26:13.071
I wouldn't call it a legend, but more like a dream.

00:26:14.306 --> 00:26:15.407
The dream of free divers.

00:26:20.579 --> 00:26:23.281
Is there a difference between the two?

00:26:25.550 --> 00:26:26.618
A dream...

00:26:30.121 --> 00:26:32.123
can come true, as long as you believe in it.

00:26:58.416 --> 00:27:01.820
Faith does not come from knowledge.

00:27:48.233 --> 00:27:49.234
Perhaps faith...

00:27:50.302 --> 00:27:51.870
is born out of uncertainty.

00:28:32.611 --> 00:28:34.091
- Thank you for the food! - Enjoy it!

00:28:34.779 --> 00:28:36.648
All right. Cheers!

00:28:39.784 --> 00:28:40.986
Come on, Duk Hyun.

00:28:41.419 --> 00:28:43.822
One more time. Cheers.

00:28:46.491 --> 00:28:47.592
- Cheers. - Cheers.

00:28:56.434 --> 00:28:57.936
These look so good.

00:29:14.152 --> 00:29:15.220
How long...

00:29:16.188 --> 00:29:17.923
do you plan to stay?

00:29:18.590 --> 00:29:19.591
Well,

00:29:20.058 --> 00:29:21.259
until my business is done.

00:29:22.093 --> 00:29:23.195
Exactly.

00:29:23.628 --> 00:29:25.597
What's this business of yours?

00:29:27.132 --> 00:29:29.133
Duk Hyun must have...

00:29:29.134 --> 00:29:32.337
stolen your girlfriend, new guy.

00:29:33.705 --> 00:29:36.408
The war of love.

00:29:37.809 --> 00:29:39.878
I guess it's similar.

00:29:40.512 --> 00:29:43.081
What? Is that really the issue?

00:29:46.518 --> 00:29:48.053
This punk, Yoon Duk Hyun,

00:29:51.890 --> 00:29:54.159
did take something very precious from me.

00:30:04.202 --> 00:30:05.570
I'm calling it a night.

00:30:06.638 --> 00:30:08.173
Wait, Duk Hyun.

00:30:15.981 --> 00:30:17.682
New guy, you just made this...

00:30:18.783 --> 00:30:19.918
so boring.

00:30:20.452 --> 00:30:21.453
What now?

00:30:22.687 --> 00:30:23.688
So?

00:30:24.422 --> 00:30:26.057
What did he take from you?

00:30:28.293 --> 00:30:29.327
Do you want to know?

00:30:37.636 --> 00:30:40.105
- It's a secret. - Darn it.

00:30:41.373 --> 00:30:42.440
Drink as a penalty.

00:30:43.642 --> 00:30:45.576
Chug it down. You have to drink it in one go.

00:30:45.577 --> 00:30:47.912
- How am I going to do that? - Bottoms up!

00:30:47.913 --> 00:30:49.681
You're so tacky.

00:30:49.848 --> 00:30:51.348
Your hair's worse.

00:30:51.349 --> 00:30:54.085
- Cheers! - Darn it. What do you know about hairstyles?

00:31:15.841 --> 00:31:19.110
Man, that stubborn punk.

00:31:26.251 --> 00:31:29.120
Is he seriously harvesting oysters in the middle of summer?

00:31:36.328 --> 00:31:39.631
You must be thinking I'd leave after you wear me out.

00:31:41.366 --> 00:31:42.534
But that won't happen.

00:31:44.236 --> 00:31:46.171
Why are you so obsessed with me?

00:31:48.473 --> 00:31:49.474
I don't know.

00:31:50.308 --> 00:31:53.211
I forgot the reason after three years of chasing.

00:31:54.412 --> 00:31:57.015
All I want to do is grab you and take you with me.

00:31:59.217 --> 00:32:00.352
I feel the same way.

00:32:02.320 --> 00:32:03.622
You asked why I'm doing this,

00:32:04.489 --> 00:32:06.057
hiding on an island like this.

00:32:11.830 --> 00:32:15.000
I started because I thought that after three years,

00:32:17.435 --> 00:32:19.271
I might forget why I began.

00:32:25.343 --> 00:32:26.811
But it hasn't worked for me yet.

00:33:01.847 --> 00:33:03.381
Hey, Duk Hyun.

00:33:05.584 --> 00:33:06.618
Are you asleep?

00:33:08.753 --> 00:33:11.056
Stop pretending like you're asleep.

00:33:14.826 --> 00:33:16.094
About Jae Hui.

00:33:18.797 --> 00:33:19.865
We may...

00:33:23.134 --> 00:33:24.202
never get to see...

00:33:25.537 --> 00:33:26.938
Jae Hui again.

00:33:31.943 --> 00:33:33.111
So...

00:33:35.647 --> 00:33:37.749
you should stop doing this.

00:33:41.486 --> 00:33:43.989
Come with me to see Jae Hui. Please!

00:33:47.759 --> 00:33:48.927
What was that?

00:33:49.694 --> 00:33:51.263
Why is he screaming?

00:34:04.409 --> 00:34:08.246
Darn it. Doing this here won't bring back...

00:34:12.717 --> 00:34:14.586
that punk you killed.

00:34:18.423 --> 00:34:19.457
So...

00:34:20.458 --> 00:34:21.793
it's time to stop this.

00:34:23.595 --> 00:34:25.263
Come back with me.

00:34:28.400 --> 00:34:29.401
Please?

00:34:33.772 --> 00:34:34.973
Darn it.

00:34:41.146 --> 00:34:42.314
That guy...

00:34:44.883 --> 00:34:46.651
killed someone?

00:34:59.865 --> 00:35:00.866
Darn it.

